00:35:01,303 --> 00:35:03,681
<font color="#80ff00">HOTEL CHILBOSAN</font>

639
00:35:03,764 --> 00:35:06,267
<i>Dia bersembunyi
setelah penipuan satu miliar won.</i>

640
00:35:06,475 --> 00:35:08,144
<i>Dia datang ke Shenyang</i>

641
00:35:08,227 --> 00:35:11,605
